{"tid":1432657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於大台可以點答，建議引用各業界聯署嘅內容作答","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:10:44.000Z","uid":217413,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c72a18be1ddc4c8fde98c0cf15ca7b1cd41f5c6","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A環節好多記者都會問大台<br />\n答咗又怕分享者混入個人意見/冇代表性，唔答嘅話記者一定會繼續追問，最終都係解決唔到<br />\n<br />\n唔係大台但又有認受性嘅答法<br />\n我覺得可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>引用各業界聯署嘅內容</strong></span><br />\n&ldquo;根據xxxx，提到「&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;」，所以xxxx&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;有xx個聯署，包括xx業、xx業等，都同時提到「&hellip;&hellip;」&rdquo;</span><br />\n每次識得<strong>引用多幾篇</strong>就更好、更全面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因有以下3個：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 有資料來源會說服力大增，亦有認受性</span><br />\n有讀過/讀緊中學嘅一定學過引用資料嘅答題技巧，引用資料嘅好處係說服力大增<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">聯署正正係代表一個群體嘅意見</span>，呢啲意見絕對有一定嘅認受性，唔係隨街執返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>同時可以對比警犬記招，唔似得佢哋係連登是但cap個圖落黎9up，一啲都唔專業</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 宣傳遍地開花嘅聯署</span><br />\n有巴打提過其實有人唔係好知道各業界聯署，就算知道都未必仔細咁睇每一篇嘅內容，而<span style=\"color: red;\">民間記招嘅原意就係代社會無能力發聲嘅群眾發聲</span><br />\n民間記招就係個宣傳聯署嘅好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 聯署數目夠多</span><br />\n我冇實際數過有幾多業界聯署過，因為實在係好多好多<br />\n我哋本來已經有大量適合嘅資料係手，只係在乎我哋能唔能夠好好咁運用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個亦係我開po嘅另一個原因<br />\n想各位巴絲幫幫手，如果認同依個做法，<span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以回覆度po返唔同業界聯署嘅link/原文？令依個po變成一個整合，方便比民間記招小組為下次記招做準備</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲認為有啲文章都值得做社會大眾意見嘅例子，可以提出黎"},{"pid":"94f8a197aff582a1add1b3c37c09f154826b1fe0","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd1a614be8277b8fef128712a5092b2ec01f592b","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5dbd15347753516396dab575b69e32845f95c84","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"5610303dabb62fabf770fd65628035f897462d06","tid":1432657,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e725b865ad444c02542a36ace98244d97677828f","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52fecc8360f2fe96a226d094ba45a085d56f04ad","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f8f94d13dd6df057a66adeb36e400b10561faf","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b43202b21cd5d7debbad216dbd85a40b31bae697","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee8dd994ad7319bffe6c70a5140baa25f737d6c","tid":1432657,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677986d9da0b29adbd17a0d49ef142d3491dd2f8","tid":1432657,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"good idea push"},{"pid":"d5c3aaf390a35fe5c0716b04128913c9a1201331","tid":1432657,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"